can we change instance type without down time?

For Instance refresh in ASG create before destroy or etc..,

Instance Refresh is an ASG feature that gradually replaces all existing instances with new ones when you update the Launch Template — like a rolling update. 
It respects minimum healthy percentage so your app stays available during the refresh.

 AWS Console:

EC2 → Auto Scaling Groups → Select ASG
→ Instance Refresh tab
→ Start Instance Refresh
→ Set Minimum Healthy % → Start

