Blue green do we say for route 53 or ASG?
--
Route 53 Blue/Green — How it Works

Route 53 Weighted Routing:

Blue:
  Record : myapp.com
  Target : Blue ALB
  Weight : 100 → 0

Green:
  Record : myapp.com
  Target : Green ALB
  Weight : 0 → 100

Switch:
  change weights in Route 53 ✅
---

ASG Blue/Green — How it Works

ALB Listener Rule:

Blue TG  (old ASG) : weight 100 → 0
Green TG (new ASG) : weight 0 → 100

Switch:
  change weights in ALB ✅
  instant! no DNS delay

-=---

