Change ALB target group weights to switch or rollback

Traffic switching:
To green → weight 0 → 100
Rollback → weight 100 → 0

Users → Route 53 → ALB
  ALB splits traffic by weight:
    Blue TG  → 100% → Blue ASG  → EC2 (ami-old123)
    Green TG →   0% → Green ASG → EC2 (ami-new456)

To deploy new version:
  Change ALB weights → Blue 0% / Green 100% ✅

To rollback:
  Change ALB weights → Blue 100% / Green 0% ✅
